'''德文郡旗幟'''是[[英國|英國]][[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[德文郡|德文郡]]的旗幟，系通過公眾募集而產生<ref>{{Cite web | url=http://www.fotw.net/flags/gb-e-dev.html | title=Devon, England | work=Flags of the world | date=21 October 2011 | accessdate=25 January 2014 | archive-date=2003-04-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030428071755/http://www.fotw.net/flags/gb-e-dev.html }}</ref><ref name=bbc_devon_flag>{{Cite web | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/devon/community_life/features/devon_flag.shtml | date = January 2005 | title = Flag celebrates Devon's heritage | publisher = BBC Devon website | accessdate = 25 January 2014 | archive-date = 2010-04-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100425161755/http://www.bbc.co.uk/devon/community_life/features/devon_flag.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。這面旗幟使用了綠色、黑色和白色三種顏色。自2003年使用以來，德文郡旗幟已經得到普及。在2006年10月，德文郡旗幟得到了官方正式承認<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.devon.gov.uk/devonflag | title = Devon Flag | work = Devon County Council website | accessdate = 25 January 2014 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140201203703/http://www.devon.gov.uk/devonflag | archivedate = 2014年2月1日 }}</ref>。 

